  "text": "In general, using cooling system is a straightforward way to reduce the temperature rise effect. According to different cooling media, the cooling systems can be divided into natural air cooling, forced air cooling and liquid cooling [CITATION_1] - [CITATION_2] . In a small power machine, natural air cooling system is usually used. If the power level of machine is high, forced air cooling will be adopted in order to strengthen the The associate editor coordinating the review of this manuscript and approving it for publication was Huiqing Wen . cooling effect. Unlike the natural air cooling and forced air cooling, the liquid cooling system uses water or oil rather than air to transfer heat to the air. The comparison of three cooling systems is shown in TABLE 1.",
